{
  "texts": [
    "Modeling and simulation is the key sub-block of building HDT in the digital world.",
    "Human modeling and simulation creates a virtual model by defining and extracting the key features of the human to reflect the key characteristics and dynamic motion of the human representation.",
    "The simulation further explores the system performance based on different modeling techniques [14].",
    "The modeling methods we explored are divided into organ and body modeling at the physical level, human activity modeling, social interaction modeling and lifestyle modeling at the behavioral level.",
    "As the core sub-block of HDT, modeling technology will be introduced in detail in \" Core technology review of human digital twin\" section."
  ]
}